en.title: [2023] Graduates
en.description: Annual graduate statistics, covering key labour market outcomes by sex, ethnicity, age, state, sector, etc.
en.description_email: DOSM has just released the latest annual graduate statistics, covering key labour market outcomes of graduates, with breakdowns by sex, ethnicity, age, state, sector, and other socio-economic characteristics.
